<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Case Resolution Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38a169 0%, #2f855a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .email-header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .success-banner {
            background: #c6f6d5;
            color: #2f855a;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #38a169;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .case-details {
            background: #f0fff4;
            border-left: 4px solid #38a169;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
        }
        .case-details h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #38a169;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .case-detail-row {
            margin: 8px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .case-detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            min-width: 140px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: #c6f6d5;
            color: #2f855a;
        }
        .resolution-summary {
            background: #f7fafc;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .resolution-summary h4 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .resolution-text {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            color: #4a5568;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background: #fff9db;
            border: 1px solid #f6e05e;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .next-steps h4 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #d69e2e;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .next-steps ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .next-steps li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-survey {
            background: #38a169;
        }
        .btn-survey:hover {
            background: #2f855a;
        }
        .btn-history {
            background: #4a5568;
        }
        .btn-history:hover {
            background: #2d3748;
        }
        .btn-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .satisfaction-section {
            background: #ebf4ff;
            border: 1px solid #3182ce;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .satisfaction-section h4 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #2b6cb0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .star-rating {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .star-rating a {
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 2px;
        }
        .performance-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #38a169;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            color: #666666;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="success-banner">
            ‚úÖ CASE RESOLVED SUCCESSFULLY - Thank you for your patience!
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Case Resolved</h1>
            <p>Your support request has been completed successfully</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear {!Case.SuppliedName},</p>
            
            <p>Great news! We have successfully resolved your support case. Thank you for your patience throughout the resolution process, and we hope our solution meets your expectations.</p>
            
            <div class="case-details">
                <h3><span class="success-icon">‚úÖ</span>Resolution Summary</h3>
                <div class="case-detail-row">
                    <span class="case-detail-label">Case Number:</span>
                    <span><strong>{!Case.CaseNumber}</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="case-detail-row">
                    <span class="case-detail-label">Subject:</span>
                    <span>{!Case.Subject}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="case-detail-row">
                    <span class="case-detail-label">Final Status:</span>
                    <span class="status-badge">{!Case.Status}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="case-detail-row">
                    <span class="case-detail-label">Resolution Date:</span>
                    <span>{!Case.ClosedDate}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="case-detail-row">
                    <span class="case-detail-label">Resolved by:</span>
                    <span><strong>{!Case.OwnerName}</strong></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="performance-stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">{!Case.Priority}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Priority Level</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="resolution-summary">
                <h4>üîß Detailed Resolution Information</h4>
                <div class="resolution-text">
                    {!Case.Resolution_Summary__c}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h4>üìã Important Next Steps</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Test the Solution:</strong> Please verify that the implemented solution works as expected</li>
                    <li><strong>7-Day Response Window:</strong> If you encounter any issues, reply to this email within 7 days</li>
                    <li><strong>Auto-Close Policy:</strong> This case will be automatically closed after 7 days if no response is received</li>
                    <li><strong>Follow-up Support:</strong> We're here if you need any clarification or additional assistance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="satisfaction-section">
                <h4>‚≠ê How was your support experience?</h4>
                <p>Your feedback helps us continuously improve our service quality</p>
                <div class="star-rating">
                    <a href="{!Case.Satisfaction_Survey_URL__c}?rating=5" title="Excellent">‚≠ê</a>
                    <a href="{!Case.Satisfaction_Survey_URL__c}?rating=4" title="Good">‚≠ê</a>
                    <a href="{!Case.Satisfaction_Survey_URL__c}?rating=3" title="Average">‚≠ê</a>
                    <a href="{!Case.Satisfaction_Survey_URL__c}?rating=2" title="Poor">‚≠ê</a>
                    <a href="{!Case.Satisfaction_Survey_URL__c}?rating=1" title="Very Poor">‚≠ê</a>
                </div>
                <p><small>Click on a star to rate your experience</small></p>
            </div>
            
            
            </div>
            
            <p>We hope we've exceeded your expectations with our support service. Your satisfaction is our top priority, and we're always looking for ways to improve.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Need help with something else?</strong> Don't hesitate to reach out to our support team anytime. We're here to help!</p>
            
            <div class="signature">
                <p>Thank you for choosing our support services!<br><br>
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>{!Case.OwnerName}</strong><br>
                Customer Success Team<br>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p><strong>¬© 2025 Your Company Name. Case resolved successfully.</strong><br>
            Need help with something else? <a href="mailto:support@company.com" style="color: #3182ce;">Contact Support</a><br>
            Resolution Confirmation ID: {!Case.CaseNumber}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>